----- INPUT -----
; Tests that .package directive correctly prepends package to class binary name.
; Input: .class public MyClass with .package com/example/test
; Expected: Binary name becomes com/example/test/MyClass (visible in disassembly)
; This proves:
;   1. Package is parsed and stored in AST
;   2. Package is prepended to class name in constant pool
;   3. Class file is written to correct directory structure (com/example/test/)

.class public MyClass
.package com/example/test
.super java/lang/Object

.class_end
